data.description: Bring your buyers with creative ideas and style. Two story corner lot with RV gate and you can walk to the park and the local elementary school. Near shopping, restaurants and convenient to MC85 and I-10. Den and half bath downstairs. Open floorplan and windows everything for natural light. Home is westward facing. Laundry is downstairs and appliances convey. Kitchen faces the backyard where you have patios, entertainment area and gated play pool. Three huge bedrooms upstairs. The primary bedroom is divine and offers views to the Estrellas from your room. A/C is less than two years old. Did I mention seller credit? This home ready for a new family to take over and make it gorgeous and all their style. Amazing lot and location. What are you waiting for?
